<H3> <TI>   Russian Coal Industry Jan-Aug 93 Performance Viewed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  944E0564A Moscow UGOL in Russian No 12, Dec 93 pp 14-19 </F>
<F P=103> 944E0564A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow UGOL </F>


