<F P=100> RUSSIA </F>
<F P=101> REGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Smolensk 1993 Socioeconomic Figures Reported </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  944F0392A Smolensk RABOCHIY PUT in Russian 3 Feb 94 pp 1, 5 </F>
<F P=103> 944F0392A </F>
<F P=104>  Smolensk RABOCHIY PUT </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [Report by the Smolensk Oblast Statistics Directorate: </F>
"Socioeconomic Situation of Smolensk Oblast in 1993"] 
  [Text] The socioeconomic situation of the oblast last year 
is characterized by the following data: 


